    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName><name ref="Teudebertus">Teutpertus</name></persName> filio
                            <persName>bone memorie <name ref="Romaldus">Rumualdi</name></persName>
                        permuta beni con <persName ref="#people/3305" key="#Bishops"
                            >Hieremias</persName> gratia Dei huius sancte Lucane ecclesie humilis
                            <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs> (…). Teutpertus cede ad parte <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs> vestre <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/610" key="#Confinia #Churches">Sancti
                            Savini</orgName>, sita in loco <placeName ref="#places/64"
                            key="#Churches">Asulari</placeName>, que est de subpotestate ipsius <rs
                            key="#Mother_churches">episcopatui</rs> vestro <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/68" key="#Mother_churches">Sancti
                            Martini</orgName>, idest una petia de terra mea illa, quas abeo in
                        suprascripto loco <placeName ref="#places/64"
                            key="#Confinia #Petiae #Landed_possessions #Wine #Fiscal_property #Mention #Roads"
                            >Asulari</placeName> prope iamdicta ecclesiam Sancti Savini, qui <rs
                            key="#Confinia">uno caput et uno lato tene</rs> in terra <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/70" key="#Churches">Sancti
                            Fridiani</orgName>, alio capo tene in <rs
                            key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Mention">terra domni
                            regi</rs> et aliquantulo in <rs key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions"
                            >terra</rs> qui fuit <persName
                            key="#Confinia #Petiae #Landed_possessions"><name ref="Teudicius"
                                >Teudici</name></persName>, alio lato tene in <rs key="#Wine"
                            >vinea</rs> ipsius ecclesie Sancti Savini; petia ipsa de vinea (…) quod
                        est per mensura ad iusta pertica mensuratas <rs key="#Size">modium uno et
                            sistaria octo</rs> (…) cum casis et omnibus arboribus suis (…). Riceve
                        in cambio duo petiole de vinea in loco Asulari, pertinentes suprascripte
                        ecclesie vestre Sancti Savini, et est tenente una ex ipse petie de vinea uno
                        caput in <rs key="#Wine">vinea</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/3307" key="#Confinia #Wine">Heriprandi</persName>,
                        alio caput tene in <rs key="#Wine">vinea</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/230"
                            key="#Confinia #Petiae #Wine #Churches">Sancti Petri</orgName>, lato uno
                        tene in terra, mea qui supra Teutperto, alio in <rs key="#Roads">via
                            publica</rs>; et illa alia petia tene uno caput in via publica, alio
                        caput tene in terra mea et vinea Sancti Petri, lato uno tene in vinea ipsius
                            <rs key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs> Sancti Petri, et alio lato tenet in
                        fundamento de capanna in vinea mea ab oriente; ipse petie de vinee (...)
                        quod est per mensura ad iusta perticha mensurata <rs key="#Size">modium uno
                            et sistaria quattuor</rs> (…) cum casis et arboribus in integrum. Ubi et
                        super hanc comutationem secundum legem direxisti <rs
                            key="#Missus_of_other_public_authorities">missos tuos</rs>, idest
                            <persName
                            key="#Witness #Missus_of_other_public_authorities #Archdeacons"><name
                                ref="Sichimundus">Sichimundo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Archdeacons">archidiacono</rs> et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Other_minor_officer #Missus_of_other_public_authorities #Priests"
                                ><name ref="Willeramus">Vuilleramo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs> et <rs key="#Other_minor_officer"
                            >vicedomino</rs>, qui ambulaverunt (…). Pena in duplum (…). <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Adalfredus">Adalfridi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive due <rs key="#Commutatio"
                            >cartulas</rs>. Actum <placeName ref="#places/4"
                            key="#Mother_churches #Bishops">Luca</placeName>. </ab>
                    <ab>Oltre ai due missi sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>:
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Aregis">Aroghisi</name></persName>
                        filio <persName>quondam <name ref="Ghisi">Ghisi</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Notary"><name ref="Giselfredus">Ghiselfridi
                            </name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>, <persName key="#Witness #Notary"
                            >[….]fridi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>, <persName key="#Witness #Other_clerics"
                                ><name ref="Flaipertus">Flaipertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs>, <persName ref="#people/211"
                            key="#Witness">Teudimundus</persName>.</ab>
                </div>
